319
00:11:49.626 --> 00:11:51.168
Sats are up with the I-gel.

320
00:11:51.169 --> 00:11:53.629
- You ready?
- Hello?

321
00:11:53.630 --> 00:11:55.422
Oh. uh. hello.

322
00:11:55.423 --> 00:11:56.924
