not just painkillers.

397
00:14:45.343 --> 00:14:47.094
Xanax. Ativan.

398
00:14:47.095 --> 00:14:49.596
- No. not our son.
- Uh...

399
00:14:49.597 --> 00:14:51.181
Well. maybe he didn't know
that he took something

400
00:14:51.182 --> 00:14:52.766
