pushed on purpose.

488
00:18:17.389 --> 00:18:19.348
That would this a hate crime.

489
00:18:19.349 --> 00:18:21.850
Yes. ma'am.

490
00:18:21.851 --> 00:18:24.019
- Ma'am?
- Doctor.

491
00:18:24.020 --> 00:18:26.188
Sorry. I'm... I'm sorry.

492
00:18:26.189 --> 00:18:28.482
